targets.rawSql:
select status, count(*)
  from dex_workflow_run
 group by status

with cte_queue as (
  select name
       , capacity
    from dex_workflow_task_queue
)
select name
     , capacity
     , (select count(*) from (select 1 from dex_workflow_task where queue_name = cte_queue.name limit cte_queue.capacity) as limited) as depth
  from cte_queue

with cte_queue as (
  select name
       , capacity
    from dex_activity_task_queue
)
select name
     , capacity
     , (select count(*) from (select 1 from dex_activity_task where queue_name = cte_queue.name and status = 'QUEUED' limit cte_queue.capacity) as limited) as depth
  from cte_queue
